There's no gap between the tabs on the issue tab panels, which makes them look kind of squished.

You could increase the padding between the labels and the tab borders to solve this, or put some space between the tabs, I reckon. See the attached screenshots.

The spaced one has the following style changes:

{code}
ul.horizontal li {
    margin-right: 0.8em;
}
ul.tabs li {
    -moz-border-radius-topleft: 2px;
    -moz-border-radius-topright: 2px;
}
{code}

The padded one has the following style changes:

{code}
ul.tabs li a {
    padding: 2px;
}
{code}

I don't particularly mind which one you use, but I think either is preferable to the beta 3 "squished" situation.

